Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使我们感到惊讶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at our own Sun's long-term prognosis
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么会在太阳系中被留存下来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and what's in store for the rest of the solar system.
