Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙特定状况下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that with the right set of cosmic conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们脆弱的星球一定可以逃离厄运\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a shockingly different fate may await our fragile planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都将会有终结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All things must end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在五十亿年后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In about 5 billion years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们挚爱的太阳将不再滋润大地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our motherly Sun will stop
