Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在临近红巨星第二阶段末尾时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Near the end of its second red giant phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳会收缩和膨胀数次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Sun will contract and expand several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次的收缩和膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With each pulsation,
