Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  在特定的条件下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However, with the right set of circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球有可能幸免于难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our planet could be spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}克雷格·德福斯特\N西南研究院
