Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带动太阳大气外层的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lifting material from the outer layers of the Sun's atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将它们释放到星际空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}out into interstellar space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当太阳进入膨胀的红巨星阶段后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When the Sun begins to expand into the red giant phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其大气外层比现在的大气更为离散\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the outer layers of its atmosphere are even more loosely bound than they are now.
