Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究数据标明如果太阳风带走\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The data indicate that if the solar wind blows off
