Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太阳的质量减少了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If the Sun loses some of its mass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其引力会变弱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}its gravity gets weaker and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球公转轨道也因而扩大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Earth's orbit is gonna get bigger.
