Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的轨道会扩大到太阳的膨胀范围以外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our orbit will expand out enough that it will miss the expanding Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而逃过被燃为灰烬的命运\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we won't get incinerated.
