Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳在减少质量的同时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}While the Sun might lose mass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与地球之间也会产生潮汐作用力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it could also have a tidal interaction with our planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这同样会导致地球被炙烤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and this could have sizzling consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该过程中至少存在两种此消彼长的影响力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are at least two competing effects.
