Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管随着太阳步入老龄阶段\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Although as the Sun ages,
