Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.39,0:25:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文学家们认为这颗系外行星能存活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronomers think the exoplanet survived
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.02,0:25:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为已死亡的主星质量的减少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because its death star lost mass,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.73,0:25:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致对该行星的引力作用的减弱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which reduced its gravitational pull on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.19,0:25:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其程度恰好使行星稍微向外偏离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just enough so that it drifted slightly outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.91,0:25:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}布拉德·海森\N加州大学洛城分校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.20,0:25:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些绕391佩贾斯公转的行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The planets around 391 Pegasi is likely to be one of these planets
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.54,0:25:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向外旋转和在被潮汐力作用向内牵引\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that sort of walked the knife edge between
